Name: Elecsys Corp
Description: DELISTED - Elecsys Corporation (Elecsys) provides machine to machine (M2M) communication technology solutions, data acquisition systems, management systems, and custom electronic equipment for critical industrial applications worldwide. Elecsys equipment and services encompass rugged remote monitoring, industrial data communication, mobile computing, and radio frequency identification technologies. It develops, manufactures, and supports technology and products for various markets under several brand names. In addition to its products, it designs and manufactures rugged and reliable custom electronic assemblies and integrated display modules to original equipment manufacturers (OEMs) in a variety of industries. It designs, manufactures and provides wireless remote monitoring and telemetry solutions to the energy infrastructure sector as well as other industrial markets. The Company has two segments: Custom Electronic Manufacturing Services (EMS) and Proprietary Products (Proprietary).
